
Next, we'll need you to enter an email for this account. This is the email
address at which our staff will contact you, should need arise to do so.

We do not, under any circumstances, share these email addresses with any
third parties, and will only utilize them for game-related contacts.

To verify the validity of this email address, a password will be randomly 
generated by our server and sent there - so, please ensure that you have 
entered it correctly, as you will be unable to log in without it.

